  "cooking_instructions": [
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Preheat the oven to 220°C/ 200°C (fan)/ gas 7, then boil a kettle</p><p>Deseed the<strong> pepper<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong> (scrape the seeds and pith out with a teaspoon) and cut into thick strips</p><p>Top, tail then slice the <strong>courgette<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong> into rounds</p><p>Add the <strong>pepper strips</strong> and <strong>courgette rounds</strong> to a baking tray (or two!) with 1/2 tbsp <span class=\"text-danger\">[1 tbsp]</span> <strong>olive oil</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and give it a good mix up</p>",
      "order": 1,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-1630426525037-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-1630426525037-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
