            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once hot, add the<strong> flaked almonds</strong> and cook for 2-3 min or until toasted and golden</p><p>Tip: Watch them like a hawk to make sure they don't burn!</p><p>Once toasted, transfer to a plate and reserve the pan</p><p>Add the<strong> basa fillets </strong>to a separate<strong> </strong>plate with the <strong>ras el hanout</strong> and rub until fully coated</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1630426539602-x200.jpg",
