    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the fish is cooking, strip the <strong>mint leaves</strong> from their stems, then chop them finely and discard the stems</p><p>Chop the <strong>parsley</strong> finely, including the stalks</p><p>Add most<strong> </strong>of the <strong>chopped parsley </strong>and <strong>mint </strong>(save the rest for garnish!) to the cooked bulgur wheat and give it a good mix up – this is your <strong>herby bulgur</strong></p>",
