    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>spiced basa</strong> with the <strong>herby bulgur</strong>, <strong>roasted veg</strong> and <strong>shredded lettuce</strong> to the side</p><p>Drizzle the <strong>warm harissa dressing</strong> all over</p><p>Garnish with the <strong>toasted</strong> <strong>flaked almonds</strong>, a<strong> lemon wedge</strong> and the <strong>remaining chopped parsley </strong>and <strong>mint</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
